 Ahmed and Zahra Indimi Zahra, the daughter of President Muhammadu Buhari and her husband, Ahmed Indimi are celebrating their 4th wedding anniversary. Taking to her Instagram page, Zahra reaffirmed her love for him and revealed that life would not have been the same without him. She wrote,
“I’ll do it all over again if I had to..
Happy 4th Anniversary @ahmed.indimi  life couldn’t have possibly been the same without you.
“Ya Allah make all spouses the coolness of each other’s eyes. Ameen ya Wadud. Je t’aime?#zahmed2016” View this post on Instagram A post shared by 𝐙𝐚𝐡𝐫𝐚 𝐌 𝐁𝐮𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐢-𝐈𝐧𝐝𝐢𝐦𝐢 (@mrs_zmbi)